-- Finance Minister Flaherty Said to Give Canada Budget Update Tomorrow
-- B y   T h e o p h i l o s   A r g i t i s
-- 2010-10-11T21:09:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/finance-minister-flaherty-said-to-give-canada-budget-update-tomorrow.html
 Canadian Finance Minister Jim
Flaherty will deliver an update of the country’s budget
tomorrow, a government official said.  The update will show the budget will balance in the medium-
term and won’t have any significant additional measures, the
official said on condition of anonymity. Flaherty is scheduled
to release the update in Mississauga, Ontario at 1 p.m. New York
time.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Theophilos Argitis in Ottawa at 
 targitis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
